item.title: How to change ip
item.dc:creator: @i0wn3v3ry i0wn3v3ry
item.description:
@i0wn3v3ry wrote:

Search no-ip in - loader, class68_sub20_sub15, class110. (The java files) Client side.

If that doesn’t work, search 127.0.0.1, or 0.0.0.0 in those same spots.

Hope I helped.
